pable! That's it! This is the phrase! I shall transcribe it onto the score-","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":35,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":35,"voiceId":"episode-r-chu2-001","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":31}],"windowDisplayName":"LAYER","body":"Hello- CHU²? You're still on the computer? Did you even sleep?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":31,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":31,"voiceId":"episode-r-chu2-002","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":35}],"windowDisplayName":"CHU²","body":"I am making a marvelous new song for our next performance. I just thought of the best phrase!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":35,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":35,"voiceId":"episode-r-chu2-003","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":35}],"windowDisplayName":"CHU²","body":"At this rate, I'd rather finish it all in one go... PAREO! Jerky! ... PAREO?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":35,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":35,"voiceId":"episode-r-chu2-004","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":31}],"windowDisplayName":"LAYER","body":"She's not here. She left to do some errands.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":31,"motionName":"nf01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":31,"voiceId":"episode-r-chu2-005","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":35}],"windowDisplayName":"CHU²","body":"What?! So who's going to get my jerky?!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":35,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":35,"voiceId":"episode-r-chu2-006","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":31}],"windowDisplayName":"LAYER","body":"Umm... Wait one moment...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":31,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":31,"voiceId":"episode-r-chu2-007","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":31}],"windowDisplayName":"LAYER","body":"Here you go. Is this the right one? I just brought what I found in the cupboard.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":31,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":31,"voiceId":"episode-r-chu2-008","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":35}],"windowDisplayName":"CHU²","body":"Excellent! I will give you half, just this once. Here!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":35,"motionName":"smile02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":35,"voiceId":"episode-r-chu2-009","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":31}],"windowDisplayName":"LAYER","body":"Th-thanks... You really like jerky, don't you, CHU²?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":31,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":31,"voiceId":"episode-r-chu2-010","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":35}],"windowDisplayName":"CHU²","body":"Absolutely! You can eat it with one hand, and it has high nutritional value. It is very much my ideal nourishment.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":35,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":35,"voiceId":"episode-r-chu2-011","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":31}],"windowDisplayName":"LAYER","body":"Well, that is true, but... are you getting enough rest?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":31,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":31,"voiceId":"episode-r-chu2-012","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":35}],"windowDisplayName":"CHU²","body":"That is none of your concern. Everything I do is for RAS.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":35,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":35,"voiceId":"episode-r-chu2-013","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":31}],"windowDisplayName":"LAYER","body":"But if you get sick, all of your hard work would go to waste, wouldn't it?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":31,"motionName":"nf01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":31,"voiceId":"episode-r-chu2-014","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":35}],"windowDisplayName":"CHU²","body":"I have been taking the minimum amount of rest I need, and I have jerky. Right now, I must prioritize our new song.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":35,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":35,"voiceId":"episode-r-chu2-015","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":35}],"windowDisplayName":"CHU²","body":"Rest is futile!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":35,"motionName":"nf01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":35,"voiceId":"episode-r-chu2-016","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":35}],"windowDisplayName":"CHU²","body":"With this undefeatable lineup of band members, we will change the world!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":35,"motionName":"serious01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":35,"voiceId":"episode-r-chu2-017","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":31}],"windowDisplayName":"LAYER","body":"Undefeatable, huh? I'm glad that you think of us that way, but-","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":31,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":31,"voiceId":"episode-r-chu2-018","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":35}],"windowDisplayName":"CHU²","body":"I'm not just saying that. Your vocal power is the real deal. I mean it.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":35,"motionName":"nf01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":35,"voiceId":"episode-r-chu2-019","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":35}],"windowDisplayName":"CHU²","body":"And it's not just you. LOCK, MASKING, PAREO... You are all first-rate performers.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":35,"motionName":"nf01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":35,"voiceId":"episode-r-chu2-020","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":35}],"windowDisplayName":"CHU²","body":"My job is to ensure that the four of you can give your best performances without having to worry about anything else.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":35,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":35,"voiceId":"episode-r-chu2-021","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":31}],"windowDisplayName":"LAYER","body":"... I see, thank you. But I am still worried about you. RAS is a five-member band, so we have to help one another.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":31,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":31,"voiceId":"episode-r-chu2-022","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":35}],"windowDisplayName":"CHU²","body":"Alright, alright... I understand what you're trying to say, LAYER. But, like I said, I really am fine.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":35,"motionName":"nf01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":35,"voiceId":"episode-r-chu2-023","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":35}],"windowDisplayName":"CHU²","body":"Besides, if I had to add another reason for doing this...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":35,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":35,"voiceId":"episode-r-chu2-024","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":35}],"windowDisplayName":"CHU²","body":"It would be that I want to hear this song already.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":35,"motionName":"serious02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":35,"voiceId":"episode-r-chu2-025","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":31}],"windowDisplayName":"LAYER","body":"You do...?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":31,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":31,"voiceId":"episode-r-chu2-026","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":35}],"windowDisplayName":"CHU²","body":"Whether it be a minute or a second sooner, I want to hear the completed version of our new song.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":35,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{